FILE 14: /home/vasu-hdd/yocto-gateway-rt/layers/meta-cclrte/recipes-realtime/rt-verify/files/run-cyclictest.sh

Complete bash script:
1. Run cyclictest: cyclictest --mlockall --smp --priority=80 --interval=500 --distance=0 --duration=60 --histogram=500 --histfile=/var/log/cclrte-rt-histogram.txt -q
2. Parse output to get max latency
3. PASS_THRESHOLD=100 (microseconds)
4. If max > threshold: log FAIL, write to /var/log/cclrte-rt-result.txt, exit 1
5. If pass: log PASS with actual max, write result, exit 0
6. Result file format: JSON with timestamp, max_latency_us, avg_latency_us, pass, threshold

